    <item>
      <title>以色列告诉联合国法院，加沙战争“可怕”，但不是种族灭绝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/gaza-war-is-terrible-but-not-genocide-israel-tells-un-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在南非向国际法院提出请求，要求对其在巴勒斯坦飞地的军事行动采取紧急措施以阻止其所谓的对加沙的破坏之后，以色列否认在加沙实施种族灭绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/gaza-war-is-terrible-but-not-genocide-israel-tells-un-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 09:48:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚总统称欧盟梦想因“外国代理人”法而面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/georgia-president-says-eu-dream-at-risk-over-foreign-agent-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚总统警告说，如果政府面对大规模抗议而推行有争议的“外国代理人”法，该国可能会失去加入欧盟的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/georgia-president-says-eu-dream-at-risk-over-foreign-agent-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 09:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特称如果有能力，他将在秋季削减英国工资税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/hunt-says-he-will-cut-uk-payroll-tax-in-autumn-if-he-s-able</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，如果经济情况允许，他将在秋季第三次削减英国国民保险，同时他重申了完全取消工资税的长期目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/hunt-says-he-will-cut-uk-payroll-tax-in-autumn-if-he-s-able</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 08:37:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着选举进入最后阶段，致命的高温覆盖印度北部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/deadly-heat-covers-northern-india-as-election-enters-last-leg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[致命的高温正在席卷印度北部的几个邦，而南部则正遭遇季风前的大雨，给参加选举集会的数十万民众带来健康风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/deadly-heat-covers-northern-india-as-election-enters-last-leg</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 08:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲科为生命而战，欧尔班对欧盟主要盟友的命运感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/orban-bemoans-isolation-inside-eu-after-attack-on-slovak-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班表示，在一次暗杀企图导致他的斯洛伐克盟友丧失能力后，他发现自己在欧盟内部更加孤立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/orban-bemoans-isolation-inside-eu-after-attack-on-slovak-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 07:37:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
